title: War of the Roses: The Blinds Were Closed in the Guest Bedroom
description: Matt was just on a fishing trip over the weekend and came home to find some out of place things that has him questioning if his wife is cheating.  The blinds in the guest room were closed and he noticed weird boot marks in the entryway.  We test his wife to see what happened over the weekend while he was gone, if anything did happen...
